「<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">明日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あす</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">明後日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あさつて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">明々後日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やのあさつて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>」と女は指を折つて、「<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">明々後日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やのあさつて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">決定</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>つたの。然しね、私は今になつて又氣が迷つて來たのよ」と言ひつゝ、首を垂れて居たが、そつと袖で眼を拭つた樣子。其間に徳二郎は手酌で酒をグイグイ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">煽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>つて居た。<lb />
「今更<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">如何</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">どう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と言つて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">爲方</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しかた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がないじやアないか。」<lb />
